[SPEAKER_10]: The apple doesn't fall far from the tree.

324
00:43:54,293 --> 00:43:55,193
[SPEAKER_10]: Thank you, Jonathan.

325
00:43:55,273 --> 00:43:56,734
[SPEAKER_10]: Jonathan Fagan on the keys.

326
00:44:02,937 --> 00:44:06,739
[SPEAKER_10]: And Jonathan will be back in a little while to play again later in our program.

327
00:44:09,406 --> 00:44:12,509
