328
00:44:12,569 --> 00:44:15,331
[SPEAKER_10]: This is my happy place.

329
00:44:17,693 --> 00:44:30,184
[SPEAKER_10]: Reading poetry, speaking before interested audiences, introducing wonderful folks to come and minister and perform and do the things that they do.

330
00:44:31,245 --> 00:44:35,669
[SPEAKER_10]: But something else that's fun for me is being at the West Medford Community Center

331
00:44:36,349 --> 00:44:43,052
