350
00:48:17,454 --> 00:48:32,908
[SPEAKER_12]: And I can go on and on with the fruitful ground of West Medford that gave us talents, cultural talents, like Terry Carter, who became our first poet laureate of the city of Medford.

351
00:48:35,311 --> 00:48:54,270
[SPEAKER_12]: People like my co-celebrant, Dorothy Elizabeth Tucker, who in her 90s gave us her gifts and talents by dancing in front of us at the Memphis Senior Center, 95 years of age.

352
00:48:56,201 --> 00:49:08,248
[SPEAKER_12]: And I wish I could have more time and recall others, but West Medford is a resource for talented people.

